text: Bashkirsky Barmak () is a rural locality (a village) in Yanybayevsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 95 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 120 km from Isyangulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Bashkirsky Barmak
